Installation Guide

This is a quick guide on installation, and updating.

1.1 Plugin Installation

To install WooCommerce Product Question plugin you must have a working and latest version of WordPress and WooCommerce plugin already installed. For information on installing the WordPress , please see the WordPress Codex - Installing WordPress. For installing the WooCommerce and configure the shop please visit the following link WooThemes - Installing WooCommerce.

Now the next step is the Extendons Product Question installation. In the full .ZIP archive you have downloaded from Codecanyon.net you will find a file called extendon_productfaq.zip. This file is the installable .ZIP archive you can install via WordPress.

Now is time to install Extendons Product FAQ please read these steps carefully.

Installing from WordPress

Follow the steps bellow to install from WordPress Admin Dashboard

•      Navigate to Plugins

•      Click Install Plugins and click Add New

•      Click the Upload Plugin button

•      Navigate extendon_productfaq.zip on your computer and click Install Now

•      When installation is done please click Activate to activate plugin

Installing using FTP

Follow the steps bellow to install using FTP

•      Unzip extendon_productfaq.zip to a desired location on your computer. These extracted files will be uploaded later via FTP

•      Connect to your server via FTP (Use FileZilla or any other FTP client)

•      Navigate to /wp-content/plugins/ server directory

•      Locate the local directory where you have unzipped the e extendon_productfaq.zip  archive

•      Upload local folder /extendon_productfaq/ to remote /wp-content/plugins/

•      To activate the newly installed plugin navigate to Plugins and click the Activate button within the Extendons Product FAQ

1.2 Plugin Updates

Update from WordPress Admin

Follow the steps bellow to update from WordPress Admin Dashboard

•      Navigate to Plugins

•      Find the currently installed Extendons Product FAQ plugin and click Deactivate

•      After deactivation click Delete to remove the old version (your saved setting will not be lost)

•      Click Install Plugins and click Add New

•      Click the Upload Plugin button

•      Navigate the new version archive extendon_productfaq.zip on your computer and click Install Now

•      When installation is done please click Activate to activate plugin

Update using FTP

Follow the steps bellow to update using FTP

•      Unzip the new version archive extendon_productfaq.zip to a desired location on your computer. These extracted files will be uploaded later via FTP

•      Connect to your server via FTP (Use FileZilla or any other FTP client)

•      Navigate to /wp-content/plugins/ server directory and delete the current plugin folder /extendon_productfaq/

•      Locate the local directory where you have unzipped the new version archive  extendon_productfaq.zip

•      Upload local folder /extendon_productfaq/ to remote /wp-co

2.2 How to Configure the Plugin

At the backend, go to Product Questions > Settings. Here you will find the following settings:

General Settings:

  • Block Title: You can set the Block title here to show on product single Extendons FAQ Top section.
  • Tab Title (Product Single Page): You can set here the tab title dynamically for Extendons Product tab.
  • Question Publish/Pending: Admin can set the default status for front-end insertion of question pending or publish
  • Frontend Question (Open/Closed): Admin can allow front-end user to submit their question or not
  • Likes/Dislikes (Open/Closed): Admin can set the likes/dislike option enable or disable form back-end setting
  • My Account Question Section Setting: Admin set the total question limit for my account page
  • My Account Answer Section Setting: Admin set the total their answers (regarding questions) limit for my account page
  • Comments Approved/Unapproved: Admin restrict user to publish comment was approved by admin or pending for admin review
  • My Account Title: You can set my account page title form here
  • My Account Tab Title: You can set my account Extendons tab title form here
  • Comment Open/Closed: Admin can set comment open or close on Extendons Product FAQ
  • Button Text: If you want to change the Have A Question button text which is display on the product single page after product price you can
  • Have A Question: If admin don’t want to show the Ask Question button on single product page you can disable from here

Email Settings:

  • Sender Email: You can set the notification sender email here
  • Notification for Client: Enable the email notification on FAQ Inserting
  • Client Email Subject: Set the subject of notification email from here
  • Email Content: Content of email of some text you want to send with email enter here

Google Captcha Settings

  • Google Recaptcha Secret Key: Go to Google recaptcha site Google Recaptcha then click on top right reCaptcha button and follow the Instructions. Register you site by giving url path and get the secret key
  • Google Recaptcha Site Key: Go to Google recaptcha site Google Recaptcha then click on top right reCaptcha button and follow the Instructions. Register you site by giving url path and get the site key
